Ontology Specification Draft

Abstract

This ontology offers vocabularies for representing activities of daily living (ADL) that can be run in the VirtualHome (http://virtual-home.org/), run-time home situations, objects, and relationships among them.

Introduction back to ToC

This is a place holder text for the introduction. The introduction should briefly describe the ontology, its motivation, state of the art and goals.
